\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Hi. What can I help you with?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Um, yeah, I'm checking to see if I was able to get a student loan.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 OK. And your name is . . . ?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Julie. Julie Robinson.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Robinson . . . Jack. Oh Julie. And what's your student ID number, Julie?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Here's my ID card.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Thanks. Well, Julie, it appears that your application arrived a few days after the deadline.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  What? Does that mean I might not get a loan?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Not necessarily. It just means that we had to wait until those who met the deadline were processed - before we knew if there was enough money for late applicants.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  And is there enough for late applicants?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Well, maybe.
 Just a sec. Let me check your status. For late applicants we go on a first come, first served basis. And, looks like your application arrived only a day late, so yeah, you'll get your loan.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Oh, that's a relief. So what now?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Well, I'm afraid your loan won't be available for another two weeks.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Two weeks! But, how will I complete my registration without my loan money? The registrar drops students if their tuition fees aren't paid by September 20.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Well, since you know that you're getting a loan, I suggest you apply for an emergency loan. That's what people in your situation usually do . . . apply for an emergency loan.

\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  And what does that mean?
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 
Well, an emergency loan's got to be paid back within a month or a very high interest rate will be charged. So, as soon as you receive your student loan, you use it to pay back your emergency loan.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  OK. Let me get this right. I take out an emergency loan to pay my tuition, and then when the student loan comes through, I pay back the emergency loan.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 Yeah, that's right, it's simple, isn't it? Emergency loans are usually granted on the same day as you apply for them, so you could get an app
lication for one now, process your emergency loan, and then go over and complete your registration today. Would you like to do that? I can get you an application form.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  Yeah, I guess that would be all right since I know I'll be getting my student loan.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid1210041 Man:}{\b\insrsid6379710  }{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 OK, here's the form. You need to sign it here }{\insrsid206644 . . .}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553 
 and here. When you've finished filling it out, take it to Mr. Schultz in the office next door. He'll tell you what to do after that.
\par }{\insrsid9245246 
\par }{\b\insrsid9245246\charrsid9245246 Woman Student:}{\insrsid9245246\charrsid2233553  OK. Thank you very much.
\par }{\insrsid2233553 
